# Polar (payments). Secrets are set in the deployment environment, never committed.
# POLAR_ACCESS_TOKEN: website-scoped organization access token (checkouts:write,
#   customers:read; events:write reserved for Phase 2 metering).
# POLAR_API_BASE: leave unset for production (https://api.polar.sh); set the sandbox
#   base only for testing.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL (above) doubles as the Polar embed_origin.
